        {
            "title": "美國民眾實際收入成長停滯 凸顯就業市場降溫制約購買力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 經通膨調整後的美國薪資水平連續第二個月停滯不前，表明<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:勞動力市場;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/勞動力市場\">勞動力市場</a>降溫，並且持續的價格上漲正在限制消費者的購買力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國勞工統計局周五發布的報告顯示，9月份全美所有雇員的實際平均時薪環比持平，同比僅上漲0.8%，與2024年年中以來最慢的同比增速持平。由於聯邦政府停擺，該報告推遲到本周五發布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年勞動力市場已明顯走軟。招聘主要集中在兩個行業，醫療健保以及休閒與招待業，失業率也走高。受此影響，薪資增幅放緩。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-de2d4c4d-751e-398f-98c0-166304580c3a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國遲到的9月非農報告揭示勞動力市場疲態 惟過時的數據難撼利率路徑</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">生產及非管理崗位員工的時薪較前一個月小幅下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五的報告將通膨數據與最新工資數據相結合。經濟學家密切關注這一指標以評判家庭支出狀況。近來美國的消費形勢更趨分化，富裕階層成為推動消費的主力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Inflation-Adjusted Earnings Growth Stalls as Job Market Cools</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julia Fanzeres.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E5%81%9C%E6%BB%AF-%E5%87%B8%E9%A1%AF%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB%E5%88%B6%E7%B4%84%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7%E5%8A%9B-135616242.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-21 23:55:54",
